ygData.messageBody:
We need to start a dialog about what we are going to sell the new jewellery
items for. I guess I will open up by stating what I was selling things for
last night, and then all of you can comment as to whether it was too high or
too low, and we will work from there.

All +2 silver stat boosters : 7p each or 2 for 13p
Jade silver rings : 9p each or 2 for 17p
Jade electrum bracers : 25p each or 2 for 45p

This being only the 2nd day after the patch, I haven't tried marketing much
of the electrum items other than the obvious seller, which is the jade
bracer. With a skill of 79 I still get failures with electrum, and I am
trying to repay the guild for the money they pumped into me to raise my
skill. Please add to this list and comment on prices!
